Zjackrum here. Been pretty hectic with semester exams and this thing other people in my house call christmas, but I've finished Chapter 4 and 5 of gladiator_story.rtf!
Check out the adventures of Tevildo, Bjorn, Hightower and Zjackrum as they covertly battle the evil Jakarta in the country's capitol: Jakarta Town!
Homepage: www.angelfire.com/rpg/zjackrum

Put in some feedback this time (didn't get any feedback from when i finished chapter 3) it makes me feel good and encourages me to write more.

As always, feel more than happy to include suggestions for the story, and if you're not in the list of characters, submit your name and some kind of character profile that I can work with.
List of characters:

Zjackrum - elf
Tevildo - mage
Hightower - Barbarian
Bjorn - thief

Bravun - innkeeper
Owahn Khaat - Saervii guy
Shifter - Jakarta officer (friend of mine)
Deathifier - Saervii cleric
Dancing Corpse - coming soon
Triad - Archer (coming in chapter 6/7)

Keep up the feedback guys!
-Zjack
